## Project Directory Structure

```
├── rtl/                          # RTL source files
│   └── counter.v                # Counter module implementation
│
├── simulation/                   # Behavioral simulation
│   ├── counter_test.v           # Testbench and test vectors
│   ├── counter.v                # RTL for simulation
│   └── cleanup_dirs             # Cleanup scripts
│
├── synthesis/                    # Logic synthesis (Genus)
│   ├── genus_script.tcl          # Synthesis automation script
│   └── genus_dft_script.tcl      # DFT insertion script
│
├── Equivalence_checking/         # Formal verification (Conformal)
│   ├── counter.do                # Conformal verification script
│   ├── libtov.do                 # Library conversion script
│   └── slow_vdd1v0_basicCells.v  # Reference netlist
│
├── gate_level_simulation/        # Post-synthesis simulation
│   ├── counter_netlist.v         # Synthesized netlist
│   ├── counter_test.v            # GLS testbench
│   ├── delays.sdf                # Timing information
│   └── slow_vdd1v0_basicCells.v  # Liberty simulation model
│
├── physical_design/              # Place & Route (Innovus)
│   ├── counter_netlist.v         # Implementation netlist
│   ├── counter.pp                # DEF/placement database
│   ├── counter_sdc.sdc           # Design constraints
│   ├── counter.scandef           # Scan chain definition
│   ├── counter.view              # View file for tools
│   ├── pins.io                   # I/O placement
│   ├── power.tcl                 # Power distribution script
│   └── readme                    # PnR specific notes
│
├── STA/                          # Timing analysis
│   ├── counter_netlist.v         # Final netlist
│   ├── counter_physical.v        # Physical aware timing
│   ├── counter_postCTS.sdc       # Clock Tree Synthesis constraints
│   ├── counter_sdc.sdc           # Main timing constraints
│   ├── counter.scandef           # DFT timing definition
│   ├── counter.view              # Tool configuration
│   ├── pins.io                   # Pin definitions
│   └── runPnR.tcl                # STA execution script
│
├── lib/                          # Standard cell libraries
│   ├── fast_vdd1v0_basicCells.v  # Fast corner timing model
│   └── slow_vdd1v0_basiccells.v  # Slow corner timing model
│
├── lef/                          # Layout Exchange Format
│   ├── gsclib045_tech.lef        # Technology file
│   └── gsclib045_macro.lef       # Macro definitions
│
├── constraints/                  # Design constraints
│   └── constraints_top.sdc       # SDC timing/design constraints
│
├── captable/                     # Parasitic data
│   └── cln28hpl_1p10m+alrdl_5x2yu2yz_typical.capTbl
│
├── QRC_Tech/                     # RC extraction tech file
│   └── gpdk045.tch               # Quantus RC extraction rules
│
└── README                        # This file
```

