## Quick Start

### 1. Set Up Environment
```bash
source cshrc
```

### 2. Run RTL Simulation
```bash
cd simulation
xrun -elaborate -compile counter.v counter_test.v
```

### 3. Run Synthesis
```bash
cd synthesis
genus -f genus_script.tcl
```

### 4. Physical Implementation
```bash
cd physical_design
innovus -init counter.sdc
```

### 5. Gate-Level Simulation
```bash
cd gate_level_simulation
xrun -elaborate counter_netlist.v counter_test.v +sdf counter,delays.sdf
```

